Package com.sails.map.overlay

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Overlay
    An Overlay displays additional geographical data on top of a map.
    OverlayItem
    An OverlayItem is a geographical object which can draw itself on a android.graphics.Canvas.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Circle
    A Circle consists of a center GeoPoint and a non-negative radius in meters.
    ListOverlay
    A thread-safe Overlay implementation to display a list of OverlayItems.
    MapJPGOverlay  
    Marker
    A Marker draws a android.graphics.drawable.Drawable at a given geographical position.
    MyLocationOverlay
    A thread-safe Overlay implementation to display a Circle and a android.graphics.drawable.Drawable at the user's current location.
    OrientationMarker

    PolygonalChain
    A PolygonalChain is a connected series of line segments specified by a list of GeoPoints.
